---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Arash Derakhshan"
  description="About Arash Derakhshan — business leader, strategist, and writer focused on execution, growth, leadership, and building effective systems."
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
>
  <div class="about-page">


    <header class="site-header about-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">ABOUT</p>

      <h1 class="brand">Arash Derakhshan</h1>

      <p class="tagline">
        Driven by clarity. Fueled by execution.
      </p>

      <p class="lead">
        I work at the intersection of business strategy, execution,
        growth, analytics, and leadership.
      </p>
    </header>

    <article class="about-content">
      <section class="about-intro">
        <p>
          With more than 14 years of experience, I have worked across
          business development, startup building, financial analysis,
          strategy, and team leadership in different industries.
        </p>

        <p>
          My career has largely been about taking on new challenges,
          creating structure where there is ambiguity, and turning
          strategy into measurable execution.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <p class="section-label">HOW I WORK</p>

        <h2>Clarity first. Execution always.</h2>

        <p>
          I believe great performance is rarely accidental. It is built
          through clear priorities, disciplined execution, accountability,
          and teams that understand exactly what they are trying to achieve.
        </p>

        <p>
          As a leader, I try to lead by example — with personal discipline,
          direct communication, and a strong bias toward results.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <p class="section-label">WHAT I FOCUS ON</p>

        <h2>Building systems that move organizations forward.</h2>

        <p>
          From owning P&amp;L responsibilities and developing business plans
          to aligning teams through OKRs, improving pricing, analyzing
          performance, and presenting strategic decisions to stakeholders,
          my focus is always on connecting decisions to measurable outcomes.
        </p>

        <p>
          I am especially interested in business strategy, execution,
          leadership, growth, analytics, productivity, and the personal
          systems that help people do meaningful work consistently.
        </p>
      </section>

      <blockquote class="about-quote">
        Strategy matters. But without disciplined execution, it remains
        only an idea.
      </blockquote>

      <section class="about-section">
        <p class="section-label">THIS WEBSITE</p>

        <h2>A place to think in public.</h2>

        <p>
          This website is my personal archive of essays, notes, lessons,
          and ideas.
        </p>

        <p>
          I write about what I learn from work, leadership, business,
          books, building things, and trying to become more effective
          over time.
        </p>

        <p>
          No noise. No endless feed. Just writing worth keeping.
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer class="about-signature">
        <p>Arash Derakhshan</p>
        <span>arashd.ir</span>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>